headline: Prediction Market Volumes Nearly Double in October
summary: Trading volume at prediction-market platforms Kalshi and Polymarket has surged 91% month-over-month to an estimated $8.4 billion, analysts at Piper Sandler found.  The rise has been fueled in part by continued sports betting activity as basketball season begins.  Last month, the start of football season powered record trading volumes at Kalshi.
